entries.s_11: Report to Sergeant Mercious Bragg of the RSF Intelligence Division. You'll find him in the cantina.
entries.s_12: I'm ready to continue with the terrorist assignment.
entries.s_20: Very well. Return to me when you are prepared to continue.
entries.s_28: Good to have your help with this terrorist attack, trooper.
entries.s_29: There you are. We have no time to waste, so I'll get right to it. Terrorists have attacked this section of Theed. We need to neutralize the terrorists and aid in recovering from the attack.
entries.s_33: Eager to start? Quite good. This part of the city is where the attack took place. Help round up any remaining terrorists in the area. I'll be in communication with further updates as necessary.
entries.s_34: Stand away, please. The Royal Security Force has this under control.
entries.s_35: Thank you and well done, trooper.
entries.s_9: Good work with the terrorist, trooper. Are you ready for the next part of this assignment?
